  "message": "build: rebuild prebuilt libs with WAMR patches applied\n\nBoth darwin-arm64 and linux-x64 prebuilt libraries now include:\n- 001-cow-linear-memory.patch (COW memory support)\n- 002-cow-interpreter.patch (interpreter COW hooks)\n- 003-macos-arm64-x18.patch (ARM64 register fix)\n\nThis ensures CI and local builds use patched WAMR without\nneeding to rebuild from source.\n\nVerified COW symbols present:\n- wasm_runtime_set_linear_memory_callbacks\n- wasm_try_alloc_linear_memory_cow\n- wasm_free_linear_memory_cow",
